{"tid":2146704,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［Haruma Miura］呢排睇番三浦春馬嘅戲","createTime":"2020-08-08T18:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T03:11:32.000Z","uid":177102,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d32621e476637d95c70af75cbf36df73e9ce59d1","tid":2146704,"uid":177102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T18:30:20.000Z","msg":"到宜家仲係未接受到三浦春馬嘅死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我唔係超級fans，係中學果陣睇戀空先識佢，可能係我第一個覺得靚仔既日本演員<br />\n冇頭髮都carry到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rtbq6W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rtbq6W.png&h=6dea09ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排多左起屋企，心血來潮想睇番佢拍嘅戲<br />\n歡迎交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.戀空<br />\n睇第三次嘅mk狗血愛情片，但我都係喊到九彩，因為弘今次真係要變成天空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6m03T3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6m03T3.png&h=39b2cc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.好想告訴你<br />\n呢套我睇過動畫版，所以今次真人版咁教左1.5倍速睇，當茶餘飯後咁睇都推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EynxOb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EynxOb.png&h=f7c1fdf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.14歲媽媽<br />\n之前cctvb一播好大迴響，不過果陣冇睇，宜家先睇番，教1.5速睇，題材好值得討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />生仔冇錯，殺仔先錯<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfiKL9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfiKL9f.png&h=94f128b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.永遠的0<br />\n日本戰爭片，cg做得好自然好靚，講述一個駕駛技術精湛嘅空軍想保命回鄉同背水一戰嘅矛盾，感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />值得睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQQdEuN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQQdEuN.png&h=1e36d50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進擊的巨人就唔睇了，利申中意動漫版<br />\n<br />\nRIP春馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692c2a8157193c4c0777aa1747614822a3a0df67","tid":2146704,"uid":67804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T19:49:52.000Z","msg":"好想告訴你入面嘅笑容好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n風早君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51db941a1abf190b5ef70292fa45cd0417f51e0b","tid":2146704,"uid":50216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:04:26.000Z","msg":"小小夜曲"},{"pid":"87187224f7324267fb235fe719be5aa19b917658","tid":2146704,"uid":177102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692c2a8157193c4c0777aa1747614822a3a0df67","tid":2146704,"uid":67804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T19:49:52.000Z","msg":"好想告訴你入面嘅笑容好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n風早君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"爽朗君<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad61ac22aceaf8afb282a73e6e8068205841dd2f","tid":2146704,"uid":177102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51db941a1abf190b5ef70292fa45cd0417f51e0b","tid":2146704,"uid":50216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T20:04:26.000Z","msg":"小小夜曲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遲d睇下先"},{"pid":"a361efd1ba3dd920c47bba8d103217d2205509b9","tid":2146704,"uid":236155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"詐騙師, 超正"},{"pid":"db918c72d9d731fafe34b9002d06b9977cb2f8cb"